    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >产品支持简体中文</h2></strong><br><br>VR Rome重现了公元320年罗马城大部分地区的原貌，您可以在2公里*2公里的连续区域内自由游览，发现著名的罗马广场，斗兽场，万神殿等建筑。作者在创作前花2年时间研究过大量关于古罗马的考古学和建筑学资料和学术著作，所有建筑都经过认真制作。在游戏中还有对重要建筑的信息介绍，您甚至还可以进入一个虚拟博物馆查看各个建筑的1：500的缩小模型。<br><br>为创作VR Rome，除了相应编程和美工技术外，还需要大量阅读关于古罗马的考古学和建筑学知识。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964460/extras/912e55a353e05c509683abe63a6f1142.avif?t=1541463856\" width=600 height=450 /></span><br><br>VR Rome复原了罗马城主要城市区域，玩家可以在一个巨大的城市区域中自由浏览。该区域从东南方的斗兽场，到西北方的图密善竞技场（今纳沃纳广场）。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964460/extras/bd1692c2211753671d70ab67c5e0180a.avif?t=1541463856\" width=600 height=410 /></span><br><br>罗马广场<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964460/extras/2a256cfb78a95f1b973bd0714c8a92df.avif?t=1541463856\" width=600 height=224 /></span><br><br>君士坦丁凯旋门（公元315年）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964460/extras/438bf8543164334e10d22062a27cad82.avif?t=1541463856\" width=600 height=224 /></span><br><br>提图斯凯旋门（公元82年）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964460/extras/3b980732aca051c426f1def17ec8a528.avif?t=1541463856\" width=600 height=224 /></span><br><br>弗拉维圆形剧场，既斗兽场（公元80年）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964460/extras/26b54570980f358473768f4d09cd4e70.avif?t=1541463856\" width=600 height=224 /></span><br><br>复仇者战神神庙（公元前2年）<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/964460/extras/89020554ea9ea277ede9664a6c2b2563